<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="trail-v">trail <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /treɪl/    美 /treɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>拖；拉</strong></h4>
<p>to pull or be pulled along behind sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A jeep trailing a cloud of dust was speeding in my direction. 
一辆吉普车拖着一股扬尘，朝我这边疾驰而来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bride’s dress trailed behind her.
新娘的礼服拖在身后。</p></div></div>